."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"You will work with complex datasets spanning the entire customer journey from lead to revenue. We're looking for someone who can find patterns in noise and translate data into actionable strategies."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8","children":"This is a full-time, well-paid remote position ideal for analytical minds who want their insights to directly impact business growth. Experience with lead generation data is helpful but not required. We'll teach you our specific metrics and methodologies. Our team relies on data for every decision, and your insights will shape our strategy."}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6","children":"Responsibilities"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"space-y-3 mb-12","children":[["$","li",null,{"className":"flex items-start","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-blue-600 mr-3 mt-1","children":"•"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-lg text-gray-700","children":"Analyse lead quality, conversion patterns, and revenue attribution across client accounts"}]]}],["$","li",null,{"className":"flex items-start","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-blue-600 mr-3 mt-1","children":"•"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-lg text-gray-700","children":"Build and maintain reporting dashboards for internal teams and clients"}]]}],["$","li",null,{"className":"flex items-start","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-blue-600 mr-3 mt-1","children":"•"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-lg text-gray-700","children":"Identify optimisation opportunities through data analysis"}]]}],["$","li",null,{"className":"flex items-start","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-blue-600 mr-3 mt-1","children":"•"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-lg text-gray-700","children":"Support A/B testing and experiment design across campaigns"}]]}]]}],["$","h2",null,{"cla